Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.80,0:00:29.10,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}提著稍有些汙漬的行李包
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.10,0:00:32.10,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}什麼也不知道 從天空降落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.10,0:00:34.92,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}從地圖的正對面 在這裡登場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:37.61,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}在這夢中憧憬的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.61,0:00:40.33,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yea Yea Yea
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.33,0:00:43.32,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The Rock City Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.32,0:00:46.30,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yea Yea Yea
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.30,0:00:49.35,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The Rock City Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.75,0:00:53.55,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Oh baby 跳吧 跳吧 跳越牆壁 With my guitar
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.55,0:00:56.24,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}直到傳達到為止 oh yeah 唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:00:58.91,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Just music 僅僅只是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.91,0:01:01.69,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}奉獻給你喔 oh yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.69,0:01:05.31,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}真的有很多相同點嗎? With my guitar
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.31,0:01:08.32,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}邊探索 Yea 邊唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.32,0:01:11.07,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Just love 僅僅只是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:13.65,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}追趕上 be free!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.65,0:01:17.25,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}My 完美夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.42,0:01:31.98,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}睡時也好醒時也好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.98,0:01:35.20,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}把夢作為同伴哦 Yea
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.20,0:01:36.78,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I wanna believe the singing on beat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.78,0:01:38.47,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\be1}most recently is like recess for me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.47,0:01:39.79,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\be1}pretty pretty please,no birds and the bees
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.79,0:01:41.46,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\be1}but ecstasy with extra cheese
